# Machine-generated eval artifacts: ignore everything under logs/ by default,
# then carve out spike-latency + spike-edge-warmup JSON logs + smoke-edge-deploy
# receipts (finding-quality, committed alongside docs/spike-findings.md and
# the ADRs they back).
logs/*
!logs/spike-latency/
!logs/spike-edge-warmup/
!logs/smoke-edge-deploy/

# Per-provider embedding backups (each ~3.8 MiB; the canonical
# fixtures/embeddings.json IS committed). Keep backups local-only —
# regenerate via `OPENAI_API_KEY=... node eval/embed-corpus.mjs` (1536-dim)
# or `node eval/embed-corpus.mjs` (384-dim Transformers.js).
fixtures/embeddings-minilm-384.json
fixtures/embeddings-openai-1536.json
